OL,6,FThe new workplace regulations in Wales
OL,7,Fcome into force from 6 April.
OL,9,FAfter this date, all businesses,
OL,10,Fcharities, and public sector
OL,11,Forganisations anywhere in Wales must
OL,12,Fensure relevant waste materials are
OL,13,Fcollected separately and disposed of
OL,14,Fappropriately.
