OL,3,CWhat are the new recycling laws in
OL,4,CWales and how much could you be fined?
OL,6,FThe new law is part of the target of
OL,7,Fthe public sector producing net-zero
OL,8,Femissions by 2030, with Wales becoming
OL,9,Fcarbon neutral by 2050.
OL,11,FThe said: "We want to improve the
OL,12,Fquality and quantity of recycling from
OL,13,Fworkplaces.
OL,15,FThis is an important step towards
OL,16,Freaching zero waste, reducing our
OL,17,Fcarbon emissions and tackling the
OL,18,Fclimate emergency.
