OL,3,CWhat are the new recycling laws in
OL,4,CWales and how much could you be fined?
OL,6,F"We want to keep materials in use for
OL,7,Fas long as possible. With the costs of
OL,8,Fmaterials rising, keeping high quality
OL,9,Fmaterials in use will help our economy
OL,10,Fand support our supply chains.
OL,12,FFor example, by avoiding landfill tax
OL,13,Fand creating job opportunities. We are
OL,14,Falready the best in the UK for
OL,15,Fdomestic recycling and third best in
OL,16,Fthe world."
